    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索战场并收集武器：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗的尘埃落定，你来到这里帮助丹堡受伤的士兵。看起来暂时没有危险。四周散落着大量武器——剑、盔甲、头盔……这是一个绝佳的机会！你可以决定帮助谁，又抢劫谁！观察周围环境，收集武器、获取盔甲，分类并挑选出最好的。当你收集了足够的装备，就前往工坊。但请记住——你的推车装不下所有战利品！  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052650/extras/2a66f898f340f87ff5652255bc724750.poster.avif?t=1768225125\" width=616 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052650/extras/2a66f898f340f87ff5652255bc724750.webm?t=1768225125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052650/extras/2a66f898f340f87ff5652255bc724750.mp4?t=1768225125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> <br>感受锻造的精神：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拿起你的锤子！切割、锻造、拆解你从战场带回来的物品！你拥有铁砧、熔炉、砂轮等多种工具！在成为锻造大师的道路上，你将面临重重挑战！你必须熔炼、拆解并锻造无数武器，才能实现你的铸造梦想！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052650/extras/95f7c0c767de79354d5e237e3a642121.poster.avif?t=1768225125\" width=616 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052650/extras/95f7c0c767de79354d5e237e3a642121.webm?t=1768225125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052650/extras/95f7c0c767de79354d5e237e3a642121.mp4?t=1768225125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>出售你的作品：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将你在烟火与汗水中锻造出的作品拿去出售。购买新的剑部件，或回收可以熔炼成钢铁的旧盔甲！赚取财富，并用它打造真正的传世杰作！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052650/extras/484f63435aa53cf81e063836118b2726.poster.avif?t=1768225125\" width=616 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052650/extras/484f63435aa53cf81e063836118b2726.webm?t=1768225125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052650/extras/484f63435aa53cf81e063836118b2726.mp4?t=1768225125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解决附加任务中的谜题:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你对主要任务感到厌倦，你可以根据有趣且令人上瘾的迷你游戏来完成其他任务。打开城堡、射击弩箭等等。积累经验，扩展技能，让您更深入地融入游戏世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052650/extras/e197dcaaa12c66808fa3ccec121b9b8d.poster.avif?t=1768225125\" width=616 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052650/extras/e197dcaaa12c66808fa3ccec121b9b8d.webm?t=1768225125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052650/extras/e197dcaaa12c66808fa3ccec121b9b8d.mp4?t=1768225125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> <br>了解丹堡王国的历史：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个世界充满了谜团与阴谋。仔细观察，一些居民可能会分享有趣的故事！聆听丹堡街头巷尾的谈话，让自己沉浸在这座美丽城市的氛围中，投身于这片充满挑战的铁之海岸世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052650/extras/1d023cf3c27bbf0b9cc25ec0601b8b57.poster.avif?t=1768225125\" width=616 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052650/extras/1d023cf3c27bbf0b9cc25ec0601b8b57.webm?t=1768225125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052650/extras/1d023cf3c27bbf0b9cc25ec0601b8b57.mp4?t=1768225125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><br>探索更多城市和战场:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >整个王国占地辽阔。其中一些是危险的战场，每天都有数十名骑士牺牲。另一方面，这里也有巨大的商业城市，其惊人的建筑风格令人惊叹。踏上旅程，到达王国最偏远的角落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052650/extras/9e177e7feb5cb53485fb9384c1e2703b.poster.avif?t=1768225125\" width=616 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052650/extras/9e177e7feb5cb53485fb9384c1e2703b.webm?t=1768225125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052650/extras/9e177e7feb5cb53485fb9384c1e2703b.mp4?t=1768225125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
